Amazon is having an operation called SalesCheck which takes input as Username and password and produces SalesProduct. 
One SalesProduct means many items. 
One item means many categories. 
One Category means many brands.
One Brand means many sizes.
One size means many shapes.
One shape means many colours.
One colour means many prices.
One price means many model.
One model means many types.
One type means many warranty.
One warranty means many replacement.
One Replacement means many products.
One product means many dresses, mobiles, electronics and cosmetics.
One dress means shirt and kurti.
One mobile means mobile name and storage.
One electronics means many Fridge, Washing machine and oven.
One fridge means brand and ratings.
One washing machine means brand.
One oven means name.
One cosmetics means cream.
